Problem:

OEDIT/EDIF creates/replaces members with bad data in the ISPF statistics
area of the directory which can cause data exception abends in PDS v8.6.

This is dependent upon whether ISPCFIGU has extended statistics set,
the existing Edit profile has extended statistics on, or the Edit
ZDEFAULT profile has extended statistics on.

Solution:

Fixes are:  For z/OS 2.2 - UA83153  Apar OA51388
                           UA83199  Apar OA51464


Problem:

When a member list is displayed and some members have no
statistics, the User ID (ID) field for the members with no
statistics can display random values.

Solution:

Fixes are:  For z/OS 2.2 - UA83141  Apar OA51497
